<title>Points d&apos;attention</title><para><table rows="6" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="yes"><para>Point  </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Détail  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><bold>Ordre d&apos;appel</bold>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Toujours : <computeroutput><ref refid="data__container_8h_1a129f017feb0712be1dcf7932e6035aa0" kindref="member">init_data_container()</ref></computeroutput> -&gt; <computeroutput><ref refid="gestion__tag_8h_1aab50a8f567be72e656120fd71f3fb435" kindref="member">init_tag_manager()</ref></computeroutput> -&gt; <computeroutput><ref refid="gestion__tag_8h_1a7301f247665ed1c0504f27602b3cf012" kindref="member">set_tag()</ref></computeroutput>  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><bold>Appel unique</bold>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput><ref refid="com__utils_8c_1adf9124e89f799fae0f55cc9ed0a94189" kindref="member">init_com()</ref></computeroutput> doit être appelée <bold>une seule fois</bold> au démarrage  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><bold>Réinitialisation</bold>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Si vous appelez <computeroutput><ref refid="gestion__tag_8h_1aab50a8f567be72e656120fd71f3fb435" kindref="member">init_tag_manager()</ref></computeroutput> à nouveau, tous les tags doivent être recréés  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><bold>Configuration matérielle</bold>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Le module CAN STM32 (HAL) doit être initialisé <bold>avant</bold> TAGCAN  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><bold>ID CAN unique</bold>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Chaque nœud du réseau doit avoir un ID CAN unique  </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
